metadata.name: Pre Fame 1977 #1
metadata.description: Pre Fame 1977 is a collection of 1,977 NFTs based on an iconic photograph of Prince taken in Minneapolis in 1977 by photographer Robert Whitman. The photo has been reimagined by fashion illustrator Tara Abbasi in collaboration with Robert Whitman.
